 possible.\"\n\nI press my face to the porthole. Below us, another diving bell materializes from the darkness, its lights cutting through the black water. The hull bears markings I recognize\u2014the facility we abandoned three days ago.\n\nPriya's voice cracks. \"Elena. The oxygen readings just dropped to zero.\"",
